{"tid":216192,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【空軍出擊】豐盛遭Glaucus狙擊 插12%後停牌","createTime":"2017-04-25T03:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T03:29:31.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d181992155ccf9e7adb26303a05d64eab0ace39a","tid":216192,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T03:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/25/112646_c770410e6c2a1a99726675a375d0593f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F112646_c770410e6c2a1a99726675a375d0593f.jpg&h=6c6385a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沽空機構Glaucus再出手，今次目標為南京富商季昌群旗下豐盛控股（607）。Glaucus表示，認為2013年豐盛借殼上市，為世界上其中一宗最大宗股票操縱案。他認為，豐盛的走勢，與德普科技（3823）、輝山（6863）、漢能（566）的一樣，以股價暴跌收場。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，如果於2016年11月14日買入豐盛，至2017年4月21日期間，累積會蝕34%。不過，如果投資者於上述時間內，每日下午3時買入，但於每日交易時段最後一刻沽出，然後翌日以相同方法將資金再買貨，期內可錄76%收益。報告指，此顯然是有人進行股票操縱。<br />\n<br />\n報告發出後，豐盛股價急跌11.9%，報2.52元後停牌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56609748&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56609748%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170425&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c8769503\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56609748%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170425&h=d5688d2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56609748&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170425</a>"},{"pid":"fbea4c1328e5295a076745b7cae6d86433ae5038","tid":216192,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"【空軍出擊】豐盛停牌 旗下兩股變替死鬼 實力建業插一成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/25/112845_3558210f051fd9aead715db67e9b6880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F112845_3558210f051fd9aead715db67e9b6880.jpg&h=fcbc690c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南京富商季昌群旗下豐盛控股（607），遭沽空機構Glaucus狙擊後停牌。豐盛旗下之實力建業（519）及中傳動（658）變替死鬼。至上午11時08分，實力建業大跌9%報0.6元；中傳動則跌5.5%報7.28元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，豐盛為主要股東之衍生集團無升跌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56609837&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56609837%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170425&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a409a51c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56609837%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170425&h=fdf2040d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56609837&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170425</a>"}]}